e of all, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Guillaume d'Auvergne IV was born on 15 March 0935, in Clermont-Ferrand, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France as the son of Robert II de Clermont vicomte d'Auvergne and Engelberge de Brioude. He had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with Humberge de Limoges. He died on 10 March 1016, in his hometown, at the age of 80, and was buried in Yronde-et-Buron, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne, France."},"et":{"15 MAR 935–10 MAR 1016":"15. märts 0935–10. märts 1016","0935–1016":"0935–1016","0930–1017":"0930–1017","0975–1032":"0975–1032","–1042":"–1042","0905–0967":"0905–0967","–Female":"Surnud","15 MAR 935":"15. märts 0935","1032":"1032","1042":"1042","11 JAN 975":"11. jaanuar 0975","0930":"0930","0975":"0975","1017":"1017","1016":"1016","10 MAR 1016":"10. märts 1016","0905":"0905","989":"0989","0967":"0967","0935":"0935","(Auvergne)":"Auvergne, Prantsusmaa","Yronde-et-Buron, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne, France":"Yronde-et-Buron, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne, Prantsusmaa","Aquitaine, Auvergne, Haute-Normandie, France":"Auvergny, Eure, Haute-Normandie, Prantsusmaa","Clermont-Ferrand,63113,Puy-de-Dôme,Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes,FRANCE,":"Clermont-Ferrand, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, Prantsusmaa","Gravelines,59273,Nord,Hauts-de-France,FRANCE,":"Gravelines, Nord, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"15 MAR 935–10 MAR 1016":"15. maaliskuuta 0935–10. maaliskuuta 1016","0935–1016":"0935–1016","0930–1017":"0930–1017","0975–1032":"0975–1032","–1042":"–1042","0905–0967":"0905–0967","–Female":"Kuollut","15 MAR 935":"15. maaliskuuta 0935","1032":"1032","1042":"1042","11 JAN 975":"11. tammikuuta 0975","0930":"0930","0975":"0975","1017":"1017","1016":"1016","10 MAR 1016":"10. maaliskuuta 1016","0905":"0905","989":"0989","0967":"0967","0935":"0935","(Auvergne)":"Auvergne, Ranska","Yronde-et-